create a button which is shown in every page using navbar when it's pressed, access a devices mic in order to get Encoded base64 string of byte[] that generated from raw data less than 500KB (3-5 seconds sample are good enough for detection). The raw sound data must be 44100Hz, 1 channel (Mono), signed 16 bit PCM little endian. Other types of media are NOT supported, such as : mp3, wav, etc... or need to be converted to uncompressed raw data. 

and it's for music detection

the api usage: 
const url = 'https://shazam.p.rapidapi.com/songs/v3/detect?timezone=America%2FChicago&locale=en-US';
const options = {
	method: 'POST',
	headers: {
		'x-rapidapi-key': 'keyin .env file ',
		'x-rapidapi-host': 'shazam.p.rapidapi.com',
		'Content-Type': 'text/plain'
	},
	body: 'Generate one on your own for testing and send the body with the content-type as text/plain'
};

try {
	const response = await fetch(url, options);
	const result = await response.text();
	console.log(result);
} catch (error) {
	console.error(error);
}